Okay, seems like some peopel dont know how to add the games to your phone, but its realy simple.
1. Connect you memmory card to the cxomputer (Use a card slot, usb blue tooth what ever) 
2. Locate the file called Other
3 put the games you want inside others
4. unconnect your storing sire
5. Go to others on your phone and select the game you want to instal
6. press install and follow instructions! Send me a message if you want to ask morte questions or still dont understand.
